         <xocs:funding-text>We thank Peter Nelson and Linda Geiser for helping us access and understand the National Forest Lichen Air Quality Monitoring Program data set. We are grateful to Tom Carlberg for assistance with this project, and we thank the Fukami lab at Stanford for early feedback on the project. We also thank Trevor Goward for valuable comments on an early draft of the manuscript. Finally, we acknoweledge the numerous surveyors whose work under the Survey and Manage program has greatly enhanced our knowledge of lichens in the Pacific Northwest.</xocs:funding-text>
